README
------
The original Affix file was created by Renier de Vos in 1993.  The license was
changed to the LGPL in 2003.  This version makes use of the unified Afrikaans
wordlist used by various spellcheckers.

Compiling
---------
Requires: buildhash - from the ispell package

Type the following in the parent directory

make ispell

This will run the hash algorithms and create a tarball

LANGUAGE-VERSION.tar.bz2 which contains:

LANGUAGE.aff
LANGUAGE.hash
README


Installation
------------
The ispell dictionary is usually installed in /usr/lib/ispell.
